<div class="sub-content-header">2nd Screen Summit at CES</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Logos/CES-828-2nd-Screen-Summit-Logo-copy.jpg"/>
<p><strong>Monday, January 7, </strong><br />
<strong>Wynn Hotel &amp; Casino</strong><br />
&nbsp;<br />
Join the 2nd Screen Society for a half day of expert, in-depth panels, educational presentations and thought leadership around the emerging 2nd Screen ecosystem and enabling technologies. It&#39;s a must-attend for executives in CE, broadcast, advertising and content and for service provider partners that are developing cutting-edge apps and companion programming. The event is produced by the Media &amp; Entertainment Services Alliance (MESA) in cooperation with the 2nd Screen Society.<br />
<strong>Please visit <a href="http://www.2ndscreensociety.com/CES"><u>2ndScreenSociety.com/CES</u></a> or contact <a href="mailto:guy@MESAlliance.org"><u>Guy Finley</u></a> for session and <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/Conference-Program/Conference-Tracks.aspx" title="Click to Continue &gt; by Coupon Companion"><u>registration</u></a> information.</strong><br />
</p>
