<div class="sub-content-header">The 2013 What HI-FI? Sound and Vision Stars of CES</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Awards%20and%20Events/CES-708WHFces2013.jpg"/>
<p>5:30 p.m. Winners Announced<br />
Wednesday, January 9<br />
The Venetian, Level 1, Casanova Ballroom 501<br />
