Centered on the high-performance audio exhibits in The Venetian, Stars of CES will highlight the show&rsquo;s most impressive debuts, from the latest high-tech streaming solutions to the very best in traditional hi-fi and AV. Potential Stars of CES winners don&rsquo;t need a big booth to impress our expert judges &ndash; just a superb new product that will excite our global readership of enthusiasts. <em>What Hi-Fi? Sound and Vision</em> has been sharing its passion for the very best in audio and video for more than 36 years. In January 2013 we&rsquo;ll have even more to shout about. Early product submissions can be sent to <a href="mailto:StarsofCES.awards@haymarket.com"><u>StarsofCES.awards@haymarket.com</u></a> and include any embargo details clearly.<br />
</p>
