<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="913"><span style="display: none">The ALMA Winter Symposium</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">The ALMA Winter Symposium</div><br/>

<p>The Association of Loudspeaker Manufacturing &amp; Acoustics International (ALMA) Winter Symposium, <em>&ldquo;Product Development in the Global Paradigm: Acoustic Modeling, Measurement and Manufacturing in the Modern Marketplace&rdquo;</em> will be held before CES, January 6-7, 2013, at The Tuscany Suites &amp; Casino, 255 E. Flamingo Rd., Las Vegas. The program will cover technologies such as micro-drivers, microphones, hearing aids, and other transducer-related technology.&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;<br />
The largest event held in the world entirely dedicated to the loudspeaker industry, the Winter Symposium will feature seminars, technical paper presentations, tutorial sessions, round table and panel discussions, an exhibit hall showcasing suppliers to the industry, and an annual banquet where the now famous industry &ldquo;Driver Awards&rdquo; will be presented to deserving recipients.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Visit <a href="http://www.almainternational.org/"><u>www.almainternational.org</u></a> for more information and to register to attend, exhibit or sponsor the symposium.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
<em>ALMA is the only international trade association dedicated to improving the design and manufacture of loudspeakers. The ALMA Symposium is where the loudspeaker industry meets to improve their skills and to network. </em><br />
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="914"><span style="display: none">Last Chance to Sign Up for a CES Floor Tour </span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Last Chance to Sign Up for a CES Floor Tour </div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Logos/Show-Floor-Tours.jpg"/>
<p>Get the most out of 2013 CES by taking an official two-hour guided floor tour.&nbsp;&nbsp;There are five to choose from: General Overview, Connected Home and Digital Health and Fitness, Wireless and Wireless Devices, Technology for Investors and Financial Professionals, and the Retailers and Buyers Tour.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Shelly Palmer and his team of experienced tour guides will help you identify and understand key technologies and services, differentiate offerings and create action items and strategic take-aways. You&#39;ll also get the Shelly Palmer Digital Leadership&trade; CE Report (a $495 value).<br />
