<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="915"><span style="display: none">Inspiring Innovations: Tech Trends </span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Inspiring Innovations: Tech Trends </div><br/>

<p>From wireless wallets to cloud-based services, app integration, digital health and fitness devices and beyond, the 2013 International CES<sup>&reg;</sup> will feature an array of top consumer technology products and trends, including inspiring innovations across a range of hot products and categories. These inspiring innovations can be found throughout the CES show floor, in both the LVCC and The Venetian.<br />
The exhibits and conference sessions across these nine categories include: Wireless Wallets, Gesture Recognition/HMI, Cloud-Based Services, App Integration, Digital Health and Fitness, Wireless Home Automation/Home Energy Management, Connected Consumers: On Demand Services, 3D Printing, Safe Driver/Connected Cars.<br />
</p>
