<a name="921"><span style="display: none">Download the 2013 CES Mobile App Today! </span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Download the 2013 CES Mobile App Today! </div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/newsletter/attendee/CES-Mobile-logo.gif"/>
<p>With CES just 3 weeks away, CES Mobile, the official app of the International CES, is your best planning tool. If you have a tablet or smartphone, or any other handheld web-enabled device, you can build your schedule and plan your time at CES on the go &ndash; anywhere, anytime! CES Mobile provides attendees with easy-to-use interactive capabilities to enhance your show experience such as alerts to keep you up-to-date with important show announcements, access to the show floor maps to find the exhibitors and products you want to see, a built-in Twitter feed so you can join the show chatter, a conference rating tool and so much more. Downloading CES Mobile is easy! For iPhone (plus iPad &amp; iPod Touch) and Android phones, visit your App Store or Google Play on your device and search for <strong>2013 CES</strong>. For all other phone types (including BlackBerry and all other web browser-enabled phones) while on your smartphone, point your mobile browser to <a href="http://m.core-apps.com/2013ces"><u>http://m.core-apps.com/2013ces</u></a><em><u>.</u></em> To learn more, <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/Show-Floor/CES-Mobile-App.aspx"><u>click here</u></a>.<br />
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="917"><span style="display: none">Help Make CES Even Better - Participate in On-site Focus Groups at the 2013 International CES®</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Help Make CES Even Better - Participate in On-site Focus Groups at the 2013 International CES®</div><br/>

<p>The Consumer Electronics Association (CEA)<sup>&reg;</sup>, owner and producer of the International CES, is seeking individuals to participate in focus groups during the 2013 CES. We are interested in hearing about attendee&rsquo;s experiences at the show and how we can make it even better. The groups will take place at the Las Vegas Convention and World Trade Center (LVCC) and participants will be provided with a meal and monetary compensation. If interested, please contact Tara Hutton, Director of Market Research, at <a href="mailto:thutton@CE.org"><u>thutton@CE.org</u></a> or complete this <a href="http://ce.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_ezchIBaGanAk5jn"><u>short survey</u></a>.<br />
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="918"><span style="display: none">Maximize the Value of Your CES Experience</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Maximize the Value of Your CES Experience</div><br/>

<p>Join the CEA, owner and producer of CES, and take advantage of all the on-site benefits available to members, including discounts on conference and attendee registration fees, exclusive member lounge access, private meeting rooms, and invitation to member networking reception. Qualified Retailer/Integrator Members participate in the CES VIP Buyer Program, affording them many extra benefits while attending CES. CEA unites over 2,000 companies in the consumer technology industry. In addition to CES perks, members have access to valuable benefits all year round including free market research, financial management services, networking and business development opportunities and representation at the federal, state and local levels from the voice of the industry, CEA. Join today at <a href="http://www.ce.org/join"><u>CE.org/join</u></a>.<br />
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="919"><span style="display: none">Travel Channel Sponsors Hackathon</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Travel Channel Sponsors Hackathon</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/newsletter/attendee/MoDevHackathon_Travel.jpg"/>
<p>Travel Channel helps viewers live their mobile lives, delivering inspiration, offering unique perspectives of the&nbsp;world around them. &nbsp;Our Travelers are Influencers, embracing technology as part of how they live every day. &nbsp;The inherent nature of mobility and travel are perfectly aligned with our viewers&#39; need to connect and share with others no matter where they are. &nbsp;The Hackathon provides us the opportunity to engage developers and marketing partners at CES with the expectation that we can find the next great application to provide utility to this audience of passionate travelers as they experience the world around them.<br />
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="920"><span style="display: none">Complete Your CES Experience by Purchasing a Conference Pass</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Complete Your CES Experience by Purchasing a Conference Pass</div><br/>

<p>The 2013 International CES<sup>&reg;</sup> promises to deliver exciting new technologies and the best in innovative products. The <a href="http://cesweb.org/Conference-Program/Conference-Tracks.aspx"><u>Conference Tracks at CES</u></a> compliment the latest consumer electronic (CE) products and technologies by delivering thought-provoking discussions on topics ranging from emerging markets, hot new content, connectivity in the home, disruptive technologies, solutions to privacy and piracy and so much more. Not sure which conference sessions to choose? We&rsquo;ve bundled most of our conference tracks into three convenient passes.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
The <a href="http://cesweb.org/Conference-Program/Conference-Pricing.aspx#allaccess"><u>All Access Pass</u></a> is an incomparable value if you want to attend a number of sessions. If content and how CE products and technology influence the Hollywood community, the <a href="http://cesweb.org/Conference-Program/Conference-Pricing.aspx#entertainment"><u>Entertainment Pass</u></a> is for you. Our most popular sessions are packed in the <a href="http://cesweb.org/Conference-Program/Conference-Pricing.aspx#cepass"><u>CE Pass</u></a> at an amazing price. Whichever pass you select, you&rsquo;re sure to get the most from your CES experience.<br />
</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="916"><span style="display: none">“Visit Me at CES!” Exhibitor Video Contest Winners </span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">“Visit Me at CES!” Exhibitor Video Contest Winners </div><br/>
